{"tid":639280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"打擊假賬號或令用戶大減","createTime":"2018-04-23T10:57:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-24T17:58:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"faf12c8c24268f7c37c7b577ab0c213c4f8e7e0e","tid":639280,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T10:57:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180423/20370125?_ga=2.137046832.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180423%2F20370125%3F_ga%3D2.137046832.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=8RN%2B%2FEQFj5W3xOX7Koq%2F49tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=a4b96a87\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180423%2F20370125%3F_ga%3D2.137046832.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=166fead7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180423/20370125?_ga=2.137046832.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年04月23日 <br />\n<br />\n打擊假賬號或令用戶大減<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180423/large/23wx1p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180423%2Flarge%2F23wx1p.jpg&h=337f892e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■馬來西亞首相納吉迎戰下月9日大選之際，當地Twitter被大量撐政府訊息洗版。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTwitter被指打擊假賬戶不力，因這是高度敏感問題。Twitter有3.3億用戶，雖比facebook的逾20億和WhatsApp、微信的逾10億相距甚遠，但仍是主要賣點，打擊假賬戶恐令用戶數字大減。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1,600萬假賬號跟隨特<br />\n<br />\nTwitter在2014年向美國證監會申報，估計5%至8.5%用戶是程式賬戶，但去年有南加州大學教授指實際比率或多近一倍，有9%至15%之多。皮尤研究中心本月中發表報告，分析120萬條含熱門網站連結的英文推文，指2/3來自懷疑程式賬戶。一家叫「Twitter審計報告」的第三方公司，亦指用軟件掃描美國總統特朗普5,100萬跟隨者後，估計多達1,600萬不是真人。<br />\n<br />\nTwitter一向容許程式賬戶，以便自動化處理推文、轉推、追隨等動作，但受到一定限制。<br />\n<br />\n部份程式賬戶用來散播有用訊息，如實時發出三藩市的地震資訊，受到認同；一些商業品牌亦開始在賬戶以程式機械人跟顧客互動，所以不能非真人就禁。為打擊俄羅斯干預美國選舉的洗版手法，Twitter在2月宣佈不再准許用戶透過多個賬戶張貼相同推文。<br />\n<br />\n法新社/路透社  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n新賬號湧現　跟隨名人　Twitter洗版黨疑入侵亞洲<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n芭芭拉出殯　老布殊穿書本彩襪致意"},{"pid":"56c677c63022e778efdc2696668b717389ad596c","tid":639280,"uid":47359,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T11:34:07.000Z","msg":"泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/193406_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F193406_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=d4bd4bc7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"96e04272d827a09b3a0139bc685a75c964ebcc2e","tid":639280,"uid":177244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T17:58:37.000Z","msg":"連登ban分身會淨番幾多account<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}